---
title: Parsley Butter Rump Steak & Cheesy Potato Mash with Rainbow Carrots & Parsnip
description: Juicy steak, velvety mash, and a pop of color—this steak and mash spectacular is pure comfort with a gourmet twist! Drizzled with rich, herby parsley butter and served alongside sweet, roasted baby carrots and parsnip, it’s a hearty meal that’s as vibrant as it is delicious. Get ready to savour every bite!

